data.description: Don't miss out on a chance to customize your forever home in the Historical Garden District.  This 4 Bedroom 3 Bath home is situated in a well-established Garden District area.  Endless amount of storage. Garden-like backyard, with a fireplace on the large covered patio, gazebo, and greenhouse.  Split floorplan and formal dining with chandelier.  Wood burning fireplace, just in time for winter.  The potential of this home is endless.
